docs.lead_paragraph: LOST--a girl of 15, between Bayonne, N.J., and Prague, Czechoslovakia--and half the world in between! In Bayonne, a Czech laborer, who had sent passage money, waited in vain for his sister; in Prague a mother, frantic at the cable that disclosed no trace of her.
